data.description: Come see this beautiful Crestview home. You will love the living area that opens to the kitchen with breakfast bar, pantry, built in microwave, smooth top range, and dishwasher. Enjoy LVP and tile in the living room, kitchen and baths. Carpeting in the remaining areas bedrooms. Upstairs: has all three bedrooms, plus the two full baths and the laundry room. This home offers a two-car garage and a fenced in back yard. Call us to schedule your showing today!
